{"tid":1707132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為彥霖兩母女尋冤","createTime":"2019-11-11T08:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T12:53:51.000Z","uid":167938,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"61c9c4d2caf73d9c02a9e754d387547bd81f87a7","tid":1707132,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:47:51.000Z","msg":"細佬咁做絕對唔係想玩<br />\n目的就係為佢兩母女攞返個公道<br />\n<br />\n我知photoshop證明唔到太多<br />\n兩張相既角度都唔同<br />\n但最起碼對照到眼鼻位<br />\n<br />\n希望香港人唔好忘記彥霖母女<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2t8GUYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2t8GUYn.jpg&h=ccb066ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地係被滅口滅門<br />\n<br />\n或者信既人會話 唔洗做呢啲野都會信<br />\n但出面呢 ？香港唔是得連<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得我on9就由佢<br />\n<br />\n小弟初心只係為佢兩個作證<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"6e6fdb81c85a98cee1e3e96fdbe953d25e282d49","tid":1707132,"uid":15696,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:48:47.000Z","msg":"天水圍男子墮樓亡 (10:50)"},{"pid":"729925bdfb3f68092aa5ab7cade2becc86817259","tid":1707132,"uid":15696,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"天水圍男子墮樓亡 (10:50)<br />\n<br />\n上午7時04分，天水圍天恆邨一名保安報案，指一名男子倒臥上址垃圾房對開，懷疑從高處墮下。救護人員接報到場，證實男子已告死亡。警方在場調查男子身分及墮樓原因。"},{"pid":"1af46096b36f2dd316d46920bedf23a1fbd217a0","tid":1707132,"uid":167938,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:50:19.000Z","msg":"你點知佢係男人？<br />\n差佬信得過？<br />\n<br />\n你係狗？"},{"pid":"b0d7d356d8eb77e1434fb1888c2980bc1059d93d","tid":1707132,"uid":167938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e6fdb81c85a98cee1e3e96fdbe953d25e282d49","tid":1707132,"uid":15696,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:48:47.000Z","msg":"天水圍男子墮樓亡 (10:50)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"咁急？"},{"pid":"de9e42509e3e2be3333f1b1b2f19de8f771886eb","tid":1707132,"uid":334824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:51:05.